<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>관리자 로그인 | 한국난원</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css">
</head>
<body class="adm-login-body">
    <form class="adm-login" method="post" action="/admin/login">
        <h1><i class="fa-solid fa-leaf"></i> 한국난원 관리자</h1>
        <p class="sub">상품·가격·카테고리 관리</p>
        <% if (error) { %><p class="adm-err"><%= error %></p><% } %>
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="관리자 비밀번호" autofocus required>
        <button type="submit">로그인</button>
        <p class="hint">최초 비밀번호: <code>nankorea1948</code> (환경변수 ADMIN_PASSWORD 로 변경 가능)</p>
    </form>
</body>
</html>
